---
---

<section id="about" class="section" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">

      <div class="about-copy reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">Online Presence, Managed Properly</div>
        <h2 id="about-heading" class="section-h2">
          You focus on the business.<br>
          We handle the website,<br>
          <span class="text-amber">email, security and care.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="body-copy">
          Your website is only one part of your online presence. Local businesses also need a domain that works, professional email, secure hosting, contact forms, basic SEO, and a simple way to stay maintained after launch.
        </p>
        <p class="body-copy">
          ReadyStack Digital brings those pieces together. We build fast, SEO-ready websites, connect the domain and hosting, support professional business email, secure the basics, and manage the technical checks monthly so you can focus on your customers.
        </p>

        <div class="pillars">
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
                <path d="M11 2L2 6.5v5C2 16.5 5.75 21 11 22.5 16.25 21 20 16.5 20 11.5v-5L11 2z" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(245,158,11,.08)"/>
                <path d="M8 11.5l2 2 4-4" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Secure Website Foundations</h3>
              <p>HTTPS, SSL checks, DNS review, trusted form handling, and a lightweight static-first setup where suitable to reduce unnecessary plugin and login risks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
                <rect x="3" y="5" width="16" height="12" rx="3" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(245,158,11,.08)"/>
                <path d="M4 7l7 5 7-5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Professional Business Email</h3>
              <p>Add email such as info@yourdomain.com with support for MX, SPF, DKIM, and DMARC records so your domain, website, and email work together properly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none">
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="9" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" fill="rgba(245,158,11,.08)"/>
                <path d="M11 7v4l2.5 2.5" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3>Monthly Website Care</h3>
              <p>Hosting, domain, DNS, SSL, forms, links, and basic SEO checks are handled monthly, with small updates included depending on your care plan.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-amber magnetic">
          <span>Get a Website Quote</span>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M3 8h10M8 3l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="terminal-card">
          <div class="terminal-chrome" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="terminal-dot td-red"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot td-amber"></span>
            <span class="terminal-dot td-green"></span>
            <span class="terminal-filename">readystack-presence-check.sh</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal-body" id="terminal-output" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Website, email and security status output">
            <!-- Typewriter injected by animations.js -->
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-stat-grid">
          <div class="about-stat reveal">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="5" data-suffix="">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">Core Setup Areas</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="100" data-suffix="%">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">SEO Basics Included</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="0" data-suffix="">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">Unnecessary Plugin Bloat</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="about-stat-num" data-count="30" data-suffix="min">0</div>
            <div class="about-stat-lbl">Monthly Care Allowance</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
